im.","roots_ordered":["سنم","مزج"],"tokens_ordered":["ومزاجه","تسنيم"],"vec_preview":[-0.07479999959468842,0.019300000742077827,0.010999999940395355,-0.05590000003576279,0.007400000002235174,-0.07559999823570251,-0.016200000420212746,0.03009999915957451]},{"ayah_id":"83:28","surah":83,"ayah":28,"arabic":"عَيْنًا يَشْرَبُ بِهَا الْمُقَرَّبُونَ","english":"(This Tasnim) is a fountain at which only those drawn close will drink.","roots_ordered":["شرب","عين","قرب"],"tokens_ordered":["عينا","يشرب","بها","المقربون"],"vec_preview":[-0.042500000447034836,0.05939999967813492,-0.10540000349283218,-0.017500000074505806,0.04149999842047691,-0.024299999698996544,0.008799999952316284,0.09709999710321426]},{"ayah_id":"83:29","surah":83,"ayah":29,"arabic":"إِنَّ الَّذِينَ أَجْرَمُوا كَانُوا مِنَ الَّذِينَ آمَنُوا يَضْحَكُونَ","english":"Surely (in the worldly life), the evildoers used to ridicule the believers,","roots_ordered":["ٱلذي","امن","جرم","كون"],"tokens_ordered":["الذين","اجرموا","كانوا","امنوا","يضحكون"],"vec_preview":[-0.03280000016093254,0.11599999666213989,-0.032099999487400055,0.0812000036239624,-0.012600000016391277,-0.027400000020861626,-0.04320000112056732,0.07699999958276749]},{"ayah_id":"83:30","surah":83,"ayah":30,"arabic":"وَإِذَا مَرُّوا بِهِمْ يَتَغَامَزُونَ","english":"And winked at one another when they passed by them.","roots_ordered":["اذا","غمز","مرر"],"tokens_ordered":["واذا","مروا","بهم","يتغامزون"],"vec_preview":[0.02280000038444996,0.09719999879598618,-0.012900000438094139,-0.019200000911951065,0.006300000008195639,-0.07100000232458115,-0.00930000003427267,0.06780000030994415]},{"ayah_id":"83:31","surah":83,"ayah":31,"arabic":"وَإِذَا انقَلَبُوا إِلَىٰ أَهْلِهِمُ انقَلَبُوا فَكِهِينَ","english":"And when they went back to their families, they used to exult over the believers (by comparing the believers’ destitution and their own affluence) and returned speaking of them with jests.","roots_ordered":["اهل","اذا","الي","فكه","قلب"],"tokens_ordered":["وا